<p style="text-align: center;"><span>照理来说 </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span>买会员肯定会省钱吧？</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span>可现实却是……</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>昨天（17日）</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong>美团被曝出“杀熟外卖会员” </strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong>引起广泛热议</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201218/450908cad0994fce9c98a70e0ef73663.jpeg" /></p>
<p><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201218/345818ea6b1548f687e530168db5f07a.gif" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
